{"title":"Welsh language scheme","public_updated_at":"2014-10-07T10:48:43Z","details":{"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>In accordance with the provisions of the Welsh Language Act 1993, Companies House provides a service for companies or Limited liability partnerships who wish to <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/companies-house-welsh-service\">conduct their business in Welsh</a>.</p>\n\n<p>Companies House agreed a revised Welsh language scheme with the Welsh Language Board on 20 April 2010.  This set out how Companies House would deliver services to its customers in Welsh.</p>\n\n<p>We published our latest Welsh language scheme on 19 May 2014.</p>\n\n<section class=\"attachment embedded\" id=\"attachment_1064225\">\n  <div class=\"attachment-thumb\">\n      <a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"thumbnail\" href=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/358044/CHWelshLangSchemeENG.pdf\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/358044/thumbnail_CHWelshLangSchemeENG.pdf.png\"></a>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"attachment-details\">\n    <h2 class=\"title\"><a href=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/358044/CHWelshLangSchemeENG.pdf\">Companies House Welsh Language Scheme</a></h2>\n    <p class=\"metadata\">\n        <span class=\"type\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"file-size\">182KB</span>, <span class=\"page-length\">13 pages</span>\n    </p>\n\n\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"attachment embedded\" id=\"attachment_1064226\">\n  <div class=\"attachment-thumb\">\n      <a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"thumbnail\" href=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/420710/Cynllun_Iaith_Gymraeg_TC_P1_1.pdf\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/420710/thumbnail_Cynllun_Iaith_Gymraeg_TC_P1_1.pdf.png\"></a>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"attachment-details\">\n    <h2 class=\"title\"><a href=\"/government/uploads/sys